==用法==
Use this template to create a [[Help:magic links|magic link]] for an [[International Standard Book Number]] without the "ISBN" prefix as usually required. For example, in a table with a column labelled "ISBN", it would be redundant to write "ISBN" before every International Standard Book Number in the column.

==输入ISBN==
An ISBN link is created by using the {{tl|ISBN}} template with the International Standard Book Number. Example:
* <code><nowiki>{{ISBN|978-1-4133-0454-1}}</nowiki></code> &nbsp; produces {{ISBN|978-1-4133-0454-1}}

In tables (or other applications) where the letters "ISBN" would be redundant, this '''ISBNT''' template may be used instead, and the magic link still gets created automatically:
* <tt><nowiki>{{ISBNT|1-4133-0454-0}}</nowiki></tt> &nbsp; produces {{ISBNT|1-4133-0454-0}}
* <tt><nowiki>{{ISBNT|978-1-4133-0454-1}}</nowiki></tt> &nbsp; produces {{ISBNT|978-1-4133-0454-1}}

